SECTION 8: MESSAGING STRATEGIES FOR DIFFERENT BUYER PERSONAS

PERSONA 1: THE CFO / FINANCE DECISION MAKER
├─ Pain: ROI justification, budget accountability
├─ Best Positioning Ideas: #1 (Pay-per-hire), #2 (ROI calculator), #3 (Money-back guarantee)
├─ Key Message: "Subscription pays for itself with first successful hire"
├─ Psychology: ROI numbers, financial guarantee
└─ CTA: "Download ROI calculator" / "See your financial projection"

PERSONA 2: THE STARTUP FOUNDER / GROWING COMPANY
├─ Pain: Cash flow management, scaling uncertainty
├─ Best Positioning Ideas: #4 (Flexible billing), #7 (No commitment), #6 (Start free)
├─ Key Message: "Scale your team, scale your subscription - no strings attached"
├─ Psychology: Flexibility, control, growth
└─ CTA: "Start free trial" / "Choose flexible billing"

PERSONA 3: THE RECRUITING MANAGER / TEAM LEAD
├─ Pain: Team productivity, meeting hiring targets
├─ Best Positioning Ideas: #16 (Productivity), #12 (Competitive advantage), #14 (AI features)
├─ Key Message: "Professional plan = 3x recruiter productivity"
├─ Psychology: Performance, output, targets
└─ CTA: "See productivity gains" / "Upgrade to Professional"

PERSONA 4: THE INDIVIDUAL RECRUITER
├─ Pain: Career advancement, personal productivity
├─ Best Positioning Ideas: #17 (Hiring scorecard), #16 (Productivity), #25 (Elite club)
├─ Key Message: "Premium features = faster career growth"
├─ Psychology: Personal achievement, recognition
└─ CTA: "Track your metrics" / "Join elite community"

PERSONA 5: THE ENTERPRISE HR LEADER
├─ Pain: Governance, compliance, team management
├─ Best Positioning Ideas: #10 (Team collaboration), #13 (Analytics), #30 (Success team)
├─ Key Message: "Enterprise plan = complete team and strategic support"
├─ Psychology: Control, visibility, governance
└─ CTA: "Request demo" / "Discuss custom plan"

