SECTION 13: MEASUREMENT FRAMEWORK

Track each positioning idea's performance:

FOR EACH IDEA, MEASURE:
• Impression count (how many people see the message)
• Engagement rate (clicks, views, interactions)
• Consideration rate (people who investigate further)
• Trial conversion rate (people who try)
• Paid conversion rate (people who buy)
• Upgrade rate from free/basic
• Retention rate (people who stay)

WEEKLY REVIEW:
• Which ideas are generating highest traffic?
• Which ideas drive highest engagement?
• Which ideas lead to highest conversions?
• Which ideas drive lowest CAC (customer acquisition cost)?

MONTHLY ANALYSIS:
• Top 5 positioning ideas by performance
• Bottom 5 positioning ideas needing adjustment
• Best messaging angles
• Best content formats

