SECTION 14: QUICK-WIN MESSAGING TEMPLATES

Use these ready-made messaging templates:

TEMPLATE 1: ROI POSITIONING
"[Company Name] switched to Professional plan and saved ₹[Amount] annually 
through faster hiring cycles. ROI: [Percentage]% in first year."

TEMPLATE 2: FLEXIBILITY POSITIONING
"[Company Name] started on Basic, upgraded to Professional in Month 3, 
scaled to Enterprise in Month 9 - zero penalties, perfect fit at each stage."

TEMPLATE 3: COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGE POSITIONING
"[Company Name] hiring 40% faster with Professional plan features. 
That's [X] extra hires per quarter vs competitors still using manual methods."

TEMPLATE 4: PRODUCTIVITY POSITIONING
"Professional subscribers average [X]% higher recruiter productivity. 
1 recruiter on Professional = 3 on Basic plan."

TEMPLATE 5: SUPPORT POSITIONING
"Professional includes dedicated success team. 
Quarterly strategy reviews. Personal hiring advisor. Zero stress."

